% Source inspiration: complement and intersection rules in the official CSG geometry guide.
% Intentional simplification: original geometry with one deliberate signed-surface contradiction.
% Expected findings: SG008 WARNING for -fuelsurf and fuelsurf in fuelcell.

surf fuelsurf cyl 0.0 0.0 0.40
surf outersurf sqc 0.0 0.0 0.65

cell fuelcell 0 fuel -fuelsurf fuelsurf -outersurf
cell outsidecell 0 outside outersurf

mat fuel -10.0
92235.09c -0.04
92238.09c -0.84
8016.09c -0.12
